## SEO Requirements (For Content Generation)

### On-Page Essentials
- Title: Primary keyword + <60 chars + compelling
- Meta description: 150-160 chars + keyword + CTA
- URL slug: Short, keyword, lowercase, hyphens
- H1: One per page, matches title
- Keyword in first 100 words, 1-2% density
- Proper heading hierarchy: H1→H2→H3

### Content Structure
```
Title → Meta → H1 → Intro (keyword) → TOC → H2 sections → FAQ → Conclusion → Schema
```

### Must Include
- Internal links (3-5 per 1000 words)
- External sources (1-2 authoritative)
- Schema markup (Article, FAQ)
- Image alt text with keywords
- Short paragraphs, bullets, tables

